ActCanada Labour Code
SubjectRegulations Amending the Canada Occupational Health and Safety Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADA OCCUPATIONAL HEALTH AND SAFETY REGULATIONS, in order to clarify the intent of the Regulations, to provide specific direction and to correct a grammatical error. The changes are administrative in nature and are required in order to address the concerns of the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations.
